[player]: I'm willing to listen carefully to whatever guidance you might offer, even if it comes in riddles.
[blind_seer_corvus]: Then listen well. The winds of destiny blow fierce and unpredictable. Seek the heartwood of the ancient tree before the night's end, for there lies a truth that may guide your path. But beware, for not all who seek find what they desire.
