Tell me, do you know the true name of the deity? For only through such knowledge can you truly begin your quest.
[player]: If you know how we might end this suffering, I beg you to share your knowledge. I will heed whatever wisdom you offer.
[blind_seer_corvus]: The path to appeasing the Winter God is fraught with peril and sacrifice. You must journey to the heart of the Frostlands where the ancient tree stands. There, in the presence of the deity's essence, you shall find a riddle that only your purest intentions can solve.

